Interface IDominoEvent

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDominoEvent, GenericDominoEventFactory.GenericDominoEvent

    public interface IDominoEvent
    Author:
    nfreeman The OpenNTF IDominoEvent interface, the interface passed to the eventHappened method of a Listener

        Gets the EnumEvent being triggered
        Returns:

      • getSource

        Base<?> getSource()
        Gets the source object triggering the event. For e.g. AFTER_UPDATE_DOCUMENT the source is the Document being updated.
        Returns:
        Base Domino object
        Since:
        openntf.domino 3.0.0

      • getTarget

        Base<?> getTarget()
        Gets the target object for the event. For e.g. AFTER_UPDATE_DOCUMENT the target is the database where the Document is being updated.
        Returns:
        Based Domino object
        Since:
        openntf.domino 3.0.0

      • getPayload

        Object getPayload()
        Gets the payload being passed by the event.
        Returns:
        Object that is the payload of the event

        openntf.domino 3.0.0
